<div class="endpoint">
  <h2>Endpoint: Server Status</h2>
  <code class="api"><span class="curl">curl</span> <span class="str">"https://cs2d.pp.ua/api/157.90.170.75:20001"</code>
  <p>This endpoint allows you to request information for multiple CS2D servers by specifying their IP addresses and ports in the URL. You can query multiple servers in a single request by separating each server's address and port with a comma.</p>
