<div class="endpoint">
  <h2>Endpoint: Upload Leaderboard</h2>
  <code class="api"><span class="curl">curl</span> -X POST <span class="str">"https://cs2d.pp.ua/api/upload"</span> -F <span class="str">"file=@/home/cs2d/sys/stats/userstats.dat"</span> -F <span class="str">"port=36963"</span></code>
  <p>This endpoint allows you to upload leaderboard data.</p>
  <ul>
    <li><b><code>file</code></b> (required): Path to the <code>userstats.dat</code> file</li>
    <li><b><code>port</code></b> (required): The port number of the server</li>
    <li><b><code>sort</code></b> (optional): Formula used to sort users [default: 1]</li>
  </ul>
</div>
